I had the weirdest dream the other night. I dreamt that some people and I were on a religious retreat, and we were studying Jeremiah 6. You know how sometimes in a dream, you see someone you know really well, they don't look like them but it just is them? well that was happening to me... but with a bible passage.. (weird, I know).. anyway so our retreat instructor told us to lie down in a ditch and pretend we were Scarlett from Jeremiah 6 (YES I AM AWARE THAT I AM REALLY WEIRD AND CREEPY). Anyway...so this retreat thing finished with us standing on this big platform that overlooked a night sky over brisbane and there was this huge storm. The thunder and lightning was right in front of me, someone came up behind me and told me that thunder was God clapping and for some reason that got me really really emotional.. Anyway I turn around and there is the mountains right in front of me.... but theres this big stadium thing and so i start walking towards it... and I see halfwayout and the used are playing a gig on the stage in there (what a fucked up lineup :P) So Jono from HWO comes up to me and he's like "Hey kayla can you take my trombone back to your house for safe keeping?" and i'm like "Yeah ok" so i grab Jono's trombone and i get my parents to drop me home where i deposit the said instrument and go back to the concert hall. I get there and halfwayout and the used have finished their sets.. so Jono comes up to me again and gives me an AllAccess like as a thankyou gift and i go backstage, and i'm wandering down all these corridors they're all twisting and turning and there are like people making out in them and stuff. I grab my bag and get a pen and my 'the used' cd out and i'm like prepared to get an autograph, so i keep walking down all these corridors and i get to this door and i open it and the used are in there all having showers.... then i woke up....

IT WAS FUCKING WEIRD! 

anyway so i decided to read Jeremiah 6 and see what it said.... This passage freaked me out : 

 "The Lord said to his people, "Stand at the crossroads and look. Ask for the ancient paths and where the best road is. Walk on it and you will live in peace."

What do you guys think? :P

Title: Depths
Author: xEmoButterflyx
Fandom: The Used
Pairing: Quinn/Jepha (My fave!)
Rating: PG-13 or R? for now anyway, rating will go up
Dedication: To the Used who inspire me in everything i do.
Notes: This is just a prologue, I want to know what you think, so i don't get enough reviews I will not continue. Hopefully this will not suck as much as i think it does.
Summary: Wow... another rape-fic in the Music Fictions communities, as if we haven't seen enough of those already. But I like seeing pretty punk boys in pain so it doesn't matter, i know i'm cliche :P 

<lj-cut text="Depths">

Quinn POV


A smile graced your lips and curved upwards into your cheeks, making the corners of your eyes crinkle. You strode towards me, wrapping your strong arms around my waist. Your hands came up to grasp the back of my head and pushed my lips towards yours. Your kiss was dominating and I could taste the alcohol on your breath, I quivered inside. Your lips lingered on mine as the passionate kiss ended. I smiled shakily at you, as your eyes suddenly lost those warm, deep blue depths and became frosty. Your lips curved into a sardonic smile.

'Oh Fuck,' I knew what was coming. I closed my eyes and braced myself for the inevitable. Your hand raised itself into the air and crashed down on my cheek-bone with frightening speed. My head whipped to the side and a whimper of pain escaped my throat as blue flashes exploded behind my eyelids. You laughed, and started sucking on my exposed neck. Your lecherous tongue, unwanted by my body, left a trail of spittle down my jugular. 

You ripped off the thin t-shirt that covered my torso and quickly set about unbuttoning my pants. I didn't struggle, you hated it when I struggled and you punished me when I did. You punished me untill I was no longer able to move. 

I watched as you started unbuttoning your own pants and I quickly felt bile rise in my throat. You kicked my knees out from under me and I dropped to the floor like a sack of shit. You kicked me in the side until I I rose to my knees, laughing at each tear that fell and each shriek of pain that emitted from my body.

You forced yourself into my mouth and I started to bite down hard in protest. Your expression grew dark and you reached down and pulled my hair warningly. I released the pressure and slowly started to suck you off. Soon after, you moaned one last time and shot your disgusting, vile fluid down my throat. I swallowed it with difficulty, and fell to the floor, dry heaving, hopelessly.

You kicked me once and I crawled shakily, over to the bed. You were saying degrading and hurtful things to me as you beat my defenseless body, but I couldn't hear you. I was somewhere inside my mind, where life was good. I didn't hurt constantly there, it was a place where you loved me and treated me like a boyfriend should. 

I lay there helplessly, comatose as you rolled me onto my stomach and forced your way into me. I felt this burning sensation in my lower abdomen and the pain got worse the faster you went.

I absently noted that someone was screaming as I listened to you moan.

"Oh Fuck, Quinn. You're so fucking tight, oh Jesus."

As you had your fun and finished up, I thought I felt something go funny inside me as you collapsed and I realised the person screaming was me. I was writhing on the bed with your vile presence still inside me. 

As my sobs quietened down, I started to look around. You'd scrambled up quickly and had stopped your torrent of insults. Your gaze was directed toward the door and my vision gravitated there too. My tears welled up again and my face heated in shame as I saw my band mates standing at the door, shocked. They'd seen the whole thing, they stood there silently with shocked and disgusted expressions on their faces. 
I absently looked at the clock on the wall, 'Oh they're here to pick me up for practise.' I also looked down at the bedsheets. 'Theres a lot of blood on here,' I thought as my vision turned hazy and my world faded to black. 

Jeph POV


I stared in shock as Quinn's boyfriend, Nick, pulled out of him and noticed our presence. Quinn's pain-filled brown eyes wandered over to us and we watched as tears fell down his bruised and battered face, as he collapsed, exhausted, on the bed. Beside me, Branden's shock wore off and he covered his mouth as he rushed to the bathroom. The sounds of his retching reached my ears, seconds later.
Bert stormed over to Nick, a dark, clouded expression on his face. His hands twitched as he curled them into fists and punched Nick. For such a little guy, Bert could pack some power. As Nick fell, dazed, to the ground, Bert continued his assault and I felt my leaden feet move towards Quinn's prone form on the now blood-stained bed. His face was pale, he needed a doctor. 

I rushed to the phone and dialled the ambulance.

"Hello?"

"M-my friend, h-his boyfriend has just raped him, he-he's unconscious and bleeding. I don't know what to do. Please help him."

I started to sob as the lady on the other end of the line asked me Quinn's address and other information, my answers automatic. She then informed me that an ambulance was on it's way. The phone slipped out of my numb fingers, as my knees buckled, sending my form crashing to the floor. 

I heard the sirens in the distance as Branden stood in the doorway, face pale and hands shaking. Bert's outburst of violence had ceased and all that could be heard was Quinn's gaspes of pain as his unconscious form twitched on the bed, soiled in his own blood.

End Chapter.

I'm back from melbourne... I had an awesome time... :D shout outs to mike for letting me stay at his house :D we had fun :D 

I'm back in brisbane, once again alienated from most of my friends....


I DONT" FUCKING CARE ANYMORE! It was the icing on a cake of despair and misery.... and I couldn't deal. And i'm still not dealing too well and this year will be one of the most important of my life and i've only been at school for one day and i'm not coping with that already. I"M SICK OF THE PRESSURE TO FIT IN THE FUCKING MOULD! Sometimes i just wish i could go back to the days when life was good, simple and before all the shit that went on at school. The things i've seen imprinted on my mind forever, and they're never going away. Events that so drastically shaped who i am today. I'm more unsure of myself, a little more reserved. People rarely actually acknowledge when i say something important, but as soon as i say something funny, silly or cheerful, they're ears are open and so are their mouths, ready to make me the butt of their jokes once again. 
I feel so fucking ignored all the time. No one really listens to what i have to say, I love my friends dearly but i just constantly feel this extra barrier that keeps me from them. And i feel like i'm constantly cheating myself, sometimes i just wish i could tell my friends how they make me feel. but they don't really care, they don't bother too much with me. I guess the fact that i just stand there and not try to fit in doesn't help my situation.

I think the reason (besides its the tenth anniversary) i'm so into the nightmare before christmas at the moment is that i can relate extremely well to jack skellington and his feelings about himself. 
Jack longs to be someone other than himself, he's searching for something but he doesn't know what it is he's searching for. he can't find the solace in his routine, he longs for change. unfortunately life doesn't always turn out the way it does in movies....

Its Christmas time and I feel like i'm not where I belong. I feel out of place, awkward, and extremely tired. I don't feel cheer. I just can't seem to lift my spirits this holiday season. I have no idea what is wrong with me, I get like this and I can never place what exactly it is that is wrong. I'm so very tired of holding my mask of happiness up for everyone. I've been doing so well lately, and I've slumped again. My shoulder muscles are tight, and i feel high strung all the time. I'm constantly worrying about everything. I'm worrying about EVERYTHING! 

I have horrible dreams that plague me, I don't get enough sleep because I swear I have some kind of insomnia. I don't know whats wrong, this always happens and i can't do much about it except try to distract myself from the feeling that something is missing inside me, hopefully, like every other time this happens, the distractions will be enough to numb the pain.
